&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About WithMe, Inc.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WithMe, Inc. delivers convenient technology-powered amenities to clients and their guests. On the forefront of innovation, we&#39;re a remote first company that emphasizes a healthy work/life balance. We are profitable, operate in all 50 states, and have been ranked as one of the 5000 fastest-growing private companies in the United States for three consecutive years. &lt;a href=&quot;https://youtu.be/-fqQ2GQPiKc?si=DzGFPMqwwh3Wn0y4&quot;&gt;Watch our employee video&lt;/a&gt; to learn more about working at WithMe and discover why we were named a top employer by the &lt;a href=&quot;https://top-employers.naahq.org/2024-naa-top-employers-winners&quot;&gt;National Apartment Association&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet our brands:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PrintWithMe&lt;/strong&gt; makes printing convenient for everyone, everywhere. We&#39;re an automated printing solution found nationwide in coffee shops, co-working spaces, and multifamily apartment building locations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SipWithMe&lt;/strong&gt; is specialty coffee made simple. Our mission is to provide an innovative and cost-effective automated coffee solution for multifamily, coworking, and other business verticals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WithMe, Inc. is actively scaling with many of the National Multifamily Housing Council Top 50 managers and owners in the country, including Lincoln Property Company, Greystar, Fairfield, Avenue5, and many others.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;483&quot; data-end=&quot;848&quot;&gt;WithMe, Inc. is expanding its Business Development team and seeking &lt;strong data-start=&quot;551&quot; data-end=&quot;620&quot;&gt;Business Development Representatives&lt;/strong&gt; to work &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;onsite full-time in our Scottsdale, AZ office&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. As a BDR, you’ll play a key role in driving WithMe’s growth by generating qualified leads, connecting with prospects, and creating new business opportunities for our Sales organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;483&quot; data-end=&quot;848&quot;&gt;This position pays $22.50 - $30.00/hour depending on experience and is eligible to earn commission. On Target Earnings (OTE) for this position is expected to result in an annualized earning of $75,000 - $95,000, depending on the base pay rate and the commission earned.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect new leads through outbound calls, emails, and social media outreach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualify inbound and outbound leads to assess fit and readiness for Sales engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule and conduct discovery calls, ensuring high-quality handoffs to Sales representatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage daily activity goals and maintain accurate CRM data in Salesforce or similar systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with regional and national sales teams to align outreach and conversion strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously refine messaging and approach based on industry trends and prospect feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to independently manage outbound cadences and qualify leads effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with CRM and sales engagement tools (Salesforce, HubSpot, or Outreach preferred).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills and ability to build rapport quickly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A results-driven mindset with resilience, adaptability, and integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Motivation to thrive in a fast-paced, high-growth sales environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
